from spacy.lang.en.stop_words import STOP_WORDS

# tokenization
tokenized_doc = dataset['clean_documents'].fillna('').apply(lambda x: nlp(x))

# remove stop-words
tokenized_doc = tokenized_doc.apply(lambda x: [token.lemma_ for token in x if token.text not in STOP_WORDS])

def extract_main_topics(x):
    topics = np.abs(x)
    main_topic = topics.sort_values(ascending=False).index[0]
    return main_topic

# Initialize column `main_topics` with NANs
topic_encoded_dataset.loc[:, 'main_topic'] = np.nan

for i, row in topic_encoded_dataset.iloc[:,:-2].iterrows():
    topic_encoded_dataset.loc[i, 'main_topic'] = extract_main_topics(row)
